{"tid":2352731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被指建最多納米樓　恒基：視乎用家需要調節策略","createTime":"2021-01-04T08:12:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T04:47:37.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb90b1a1e3207946810a60ff23551a678ce7d9b","tid":2352731,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eaLiEdJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeaLiEdJ.jpg&h=5114c6e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恒基地產回覆，本港不少家庭和年輕置業者，對細單位有一定的需求。（港台圖片）<br />\n<br />\n本土研究社發現，恒基地產在2010至19年的10年內，興建2858個納米單位，屬興建「納米樓」單位最多的地產商，佔整體納米單位的3成多，形容是「納米地產王」。恒基地產回覆查詢時說，本港樓市以用家為主導，當中不少為小家庭和年輕的置業者，對細單位有一定的需求。<br />\n<br />\n恒地強調，集團十分重視樓盤的配套，如會所、健身和休憩設施等，以提升住戶的整體生活質素，亦會密切注視市場的供求變化，視乎用家的需要，適當地調節和制定未來策略。<br />\n<br />\n本土研究社將「納米樓」定義為面積260呎或以下的單位。團體指出，由2010年至19年期間，總共有8550個「納米單位」推出市場，而單位的平均面積亦不斷下降，由2010年的220呎，下降至2019年的213呎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568542-20210104.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568542-20210104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=054dba4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568542-20210104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=77b67fbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568542-20210104.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"95a811cf204e62060a8b6b2ca31612fb51d03eef","tid":2352731,"uid":7482,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多撚謝"},{"pid":"6ebce44aec27b2015485d39505f4a28e52ca572e","tid":2352731,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:19:15.000Z","msg":"係咪要感恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f44d7afaa311b19d7c1b42f6677107ff4bec45c","tid":2352731,"uid":70629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/enUrov7XPp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FenUrov7XPp8&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=306e1ccb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/enUrov7XPp8</a><br />\n<br />\n經典回顧：紫禁城咁大 皇帝都係瞓一張床 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a14a0eb4af0e2e04cefd56d0f7344f6c6f90a5","tid":2352731,"uid":80413,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:36:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e8de8cdb463d27b59d373affd02558919c87ec0","tid":2352731,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:47:37.000Z","msg":"要問下政府點解一大半地攞去起公屋、私樓愈冇地就愈貴"}]}